iples and Peter that he goeth before you into Galilee: there shall ye see him, as he said unto you.","year":33},{"id":"recyjW0pjOWSalmna","ref":"Mark.16.8","text":"And they went out quickly, and fled from the sepulchre; for they trembled and were amazed: neither said they any thing to any man; for they were afraid.","year":33}]}
